      <title>德国梅尔茨承诺限制移民并恢复增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/germany-s-merz-promises-to-limit-migration-and-restore-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国大选中保守党领跑者弗里德里希·梅尔茨誓言，尽管遭到公众抗议，但仍将坚持推行备受争议的限制移民计划，并恢复德国疲弱的经济的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/germany-s-merz-promises-to-limit-migration-and-restore-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:23:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁和美国钢铁公司将拜登阻挠合并归咎于政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/nippon-us-steel-blame-politics-for-biden-s-blocking-of-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法庭文件显示，新日本制铁公司和美国钢铁公司将前总统乔·拜登阻​​止其价值 141 亿美元的合并计划归咎于政治因素和审查程序失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/nippon-us-steel-blame-politics-for-biden-s-blocking-of-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
